# Everything under this directory is local-only by default — it derives
# from the user's copyrighted OPR PDF library and must never reach the
# git remote. Artifacts to keep ignored:
#
#   corpus.db / corpus.db-*   — ingested SQLite index of every PDF
#   manifest.json             — cache-invalidation metadata
#   ingest.log                — ingest run log
#   dumps/                    — per-PDF parser output (contains
#                               unit/equipment/upgrade text from PDFs)
#   pdf_text/                 — plain-text PDF extracts for agents
#   agent_briefs/             — pre-sampled claim briefs (also embed
#                               text from PDFs)
#   bucket-*.json             — PDF-path partitions used by the
#                               legacy partitioner
#
# What IS tracked: the small Python scripts that build the cache and
# the validation report explaining what the spot-check pipeline does.
# These contain no copyrighted text; they only reference the corpus
# layout.

corpus.db
corpus.db-*
manifest.json
ingest.log
dumps/
pdf_text/
agent_briefs/
bucket-*.json
